reviewText: Was a Christmas present for my 10 yr old granddaughter. She absolutely loved it. There was nothing not to like

The video is fine, and my son loves the Geronimo Stilton cartoons. However, there are only four episodes on one DVD and they are a selection from the regular season and not new episodes - as I mistakenly thought. Don't waste your $; buy the full volumes if you want to see Geronimo Stilton.
